# Multiline editing

## Multiple editing cursor with mouse
Ctrl + Alt + Shift + Right Click


## Multiple editing cursor spanning multiple lines
Ctrl + Ctrl (Hold) + Up|Down

## Select next word occurancy
(Windows/Linux) Alt + J
(MacOSX) Alt + G
## Remove last occurency
(Windows/Linux) Alt + Shift + J
(MacOSX) Alt + Shift + G
## Select all occurancies
(Windows/Linux) Alt + Ctrl + Shift + J
(MaxOSX) Command + Alt + G
